						<div class="postbody">Don't forget that some games cycle the palette to achieve animation in backgrounds. Isn't that what happens in Mega Man 2's Metal Man stage? I know there are other examples but I can't think of them now. Ofcourse it's not going to be the desired solution for everything, but it is another option.</div>

