						<div class="postbody">A better idea is to divide it further. The rule of thumb is that it's safe to upload 2 lines of a nametable and still have to not worry about unrolling anything while having time for other updates as well (attribute, palette, sprite DMA).<br /><br />Only use &quot;tricky fast&quot; techniques if you need them in the 1st place. Not that they aren't cool, but why use them if you don't need them ?</div>

